Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.38,0:00:20.41,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.71,0:00:22.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.09,0:00:30.08,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.89,0:00:40.55,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.55,0:00:43.98,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:49.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.52,0:00:55.79,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.79,0:01:02.75,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.75,0:01:07.08,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.08,0:01:09.41,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.41,0:01:16.51,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.44,0:01:26.64,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.64,0:01:30.23,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:35.78,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:41.99,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, \Nlet's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:49.04,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:53.17,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:55.63,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.63,0:02:00.01,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:02.97,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.97,0:02:04.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.76,0:02:06.23,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:07.89,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:09.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.06,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.27,0:02:12.98,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:14.48,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.48,0:02:15.65,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.65,0:02:19.78,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.78,0:02:22.20,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:26.49,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.49,0:02:29.00,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:32.93,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.93,0:02:35.29,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.29,0:02:39.51,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:42.63,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.86,0:02:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.96,0:02:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:02:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.75,0:03:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy \Nwhose body turned to rubber
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.72,0:03:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.61,0:03:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become \Nthe next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.47,0:03:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.41,0:03:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and \Nless able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.45,0:03:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.30,0:03:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.34,0:03:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabaody Archipelago!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.14,0:03:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Realizing that their ship needs to be \Ncoated in order to reach Fish-Man Island,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.83,0:03:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Straw Hat crew and Hachi's group \Nstopped by the Sabaody Archipelago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for the unveiling! \NTake a good look!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.41,0:03:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, Camie, a mermaid accompanying them,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.47,0:03:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,found herself kidnapped and auctioned off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,500 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll buy it for 500 million Berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.31,0:04:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Straw! You guys'll \Nget in huge trouble too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You annoy me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit your squirming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be all right. Just stay still.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Camie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.73,0:05:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He took the collar off barehanded?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.86,0:05:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to the help of Rayleigh, a coating \Ncraftsman who suddenly appeared,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.01,0:05:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and company succeeded \Nin rescuing Camie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.67,0:05:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.32,0:05:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, you criminals! Release \Nthe Roswald family at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.01,0:05:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An admiral will be arriving shortly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.25,0:05:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.19,0:05:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Repel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.94,0:05:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's this circle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.23,0:05:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shambles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out! All three of 'em have powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Break Through the Siege! The \NNavy vs. the Three Captains"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.94,0:06:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rescue team has arrived at the back \Nentrance! Now entering the building!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.78,0:06:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rescue team has made it inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.83,0:06:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All soldiers will commence attack \Nas soon as the hostages are secured!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.38,0:06:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! On the double!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.07,0:07:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rescue team has reached the stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are! Should we capture them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.38,0:07:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we can't! Our orders \Nare to secure the hostages!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.53,0:07:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Celestial Dragons' lives \Ntake precedence over all else!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.94,0:07:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to ascertain their well-being first!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe mortars don't \Nwork on any of them...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They really do live up \Nto their notorious names!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.71,0:07:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be impressed! \NHold out until the admiral arrives!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like we can really wait that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.16,0:07:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A head!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't drop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.48,0:07:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you talking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.04,0:07:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno! My body feels \Nhot for some reason, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Body?! What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.72,0:07:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's body is burning up over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.75,0:08:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's burning up! My body's burning up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.20,0:08:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! You can feel it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.68,0:08:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww! Oww! Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.87,0:08:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone! Pour water on it, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.95,0:08:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was a goner...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.87,0:08:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy! Don't enter the circles he makes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.70,0:08:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.87,0:08:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You mean this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.47,0:08:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, just like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.55,0:08:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.05,0:08:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.19,0:08:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make yourselves comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.79,0:08:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This'll be over before you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.91,0:08:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Third Gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.90,0:08:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bone Balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the arm of a giant!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.58,0:08:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be scared! Ready your \Nweapons! Fire! Fire like crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.88,0:08:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Brigadier General! Our weapons...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.07,0:08:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...are flying away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.94,0:09:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.42,0:09:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.24,0:09:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.29,0:09:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.43,0:09:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.71,0:09:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be admiring people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.75,0:10:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Those are my legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.95,0:10:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then whose are those?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.28,0:10:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have too many chests!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.77,0:10:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.60,0:10:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Giant Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.25,0:10:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.14,0:10:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, now! This, already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! I don't believe my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.67,0:10:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure know how to go berserk, Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.31,0:10:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're quite reliable, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an impatient bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.24,0:11:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that, Straw Hat-ya? \NThat's not a very good finish...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.14,0:11:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.11,0:11:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their formations don't amount to crap now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.35,0:11:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brigadier General! It appears all the \Npirates have exited the auction house!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.67,0:11:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They intend to escape! Don't let \Nthese runts make mockeries of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.01,0:11:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have plenty more reinforcements!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The three hostages have been \Nsecured at the back entrance!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.73,0:11:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aim the mortars at those without powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.55,0:11:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Firing squads to the rear! We're \Nnow commencing our all-out attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take those pirates down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.44,0:12:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go. They got no plan at \Nall. It's a free-for-all now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I'm back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.51,0:12:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, Straw Hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.84,0:12:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I got a chance to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.86,0:12:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But next time we meet, \NI won't show any mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.96,0:12:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm going to find the One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.99,0:12:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kid! What're you \Njust standing there for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.57,0:12:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Killer...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.12,0:13:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On our journey up to this point, \Nwe've been laughed at and ridiculed
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,whenever we mentioned getting \Nour hands on the One Piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.24,0:13:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And each time that happened, I \Nslaughtered everyone who laughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.92,0:13:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what lies ahead is a sea of death
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for those who don't got \Nthe guts to mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.66,0:13:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's meet again in the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.13,0:13:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, men!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.94,0:13:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.22,0:13:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trafalgar Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.51,0:13:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you toy with my comrades earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.16,0:13:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bepo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.74,0:14:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You're going back inside, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.36,0:14:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.33,0:14:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! It's time for us to go, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.19,0:14:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.58,0:14:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.83,0:14:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Young Master and friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.54,0:14:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flying Fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.86,0:15:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Did you just say "handsome"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.01,0:15:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I didn't. Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.87,0:15:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we're all set to escape! Right, men?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.83,0:15:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Life is rosy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.86,0:15:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't expecting help from them again, \Nbut I guess we are in a hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I have no choice...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat's getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.11,0:15:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lullaby Flanc!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.69,0:15:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Escape while you can, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.24,0:15:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit sleepin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.18,0:15:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys with those pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.83,0:15:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, not us! We aren't pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.25,0:15:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nueve Fleurs!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.88,0:15:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twist!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that was scary...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.99,0:16:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Head!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.10,0:16:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have trauma from nearly being killed \Nby Navy Headquarters, and yet...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.74,0:16:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You endured it anyway! \NWhat a fantastic person!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Q-Quiet! This is no time to talk \Nabout trauma or anything else!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.35,0:16:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We owe the young master our lives! We \Nhafta help him out of this trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.58,0:16:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Multi-shot! Flame Star! Flame Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.62,0:16:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Colonnade Rose!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.86,0:16:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man! Franky! Go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! I appreciate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.77,0:16:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let 'em escape! After 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.70,0:16:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many of these guys are there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.55,0:16:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is certainly exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:16:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're one lively old geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:16:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hurry, you three!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.05,0:16:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.85,0:17:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let the Straw Hat crew escape! \NThey're the main criminals!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.67,0:17:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.88,0:17:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thunderbolt Tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.03,0:17:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.57,0:17:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just freed Saint Roswald's slave!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.11,0:17:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did he uncuff him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.24,0:17:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you come along with me, \Npirate captain Jean Bart?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.71,0:17:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time since \NI've been called that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.87,0:18:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it means I can be free \Nfrom the Celestial Dragons...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.57,0:18:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll gladly serve under you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give half of your thanks to Straw Hat-ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let 'em get away! After 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.03,0:18:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.58,0:18:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! It's up to you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.58,0:18:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.61,0:18:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them escape! Fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.81,0:18:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Can't this slowpoke cow go any faster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.79,0:18:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this is his top speed...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.50,0:18:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've caught up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we speed this thing up somehow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They fled that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.61,0:19:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.95,0:19:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're still chasing us, even \Nafter we demolished the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.66,0:19:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course they are. There should \Nbe soldiers back in town, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.06,0:19:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get the hell off these islands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.34,0:19:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.92,0:19:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.51,0:19:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he doing on these islands?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.71,0:19:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an agile bear! He's too much to handle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.47,0:19:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it even talking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.77,0:19:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:20:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's weak-hearted!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.22,0:20:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, Bepo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.85,0:20:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! They destroyed the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.78,0:20:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a new guy, which \Nmeans you rank under me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.09,0:20:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I'm not a slave, \Nanything's fine with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.78,0:20:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did we manage to lose them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.55,0:20:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's go straight \Nto the amusement park now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.17,0:20:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you crazy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.98,0:20:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.06,0:20:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How pleasant!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.72,0:20:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite skilled to be able to \Nremodel it in such a short time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.88,0:21:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's for sure! You're \Namazing! It's so fast now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.93,0:21:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do what I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.63,0:21:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where Peterman's hideout is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.63,0:21:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peterman?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.82,0:21:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.54,0:21:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eustass-ya and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.47,0:21:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.38,0:21:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is a Warlord of the Sea doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.65,0:22:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trafalgar Law...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.68,0:22:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.13,0:22:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.06,0:22:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're right next to Navy \NHeadquarters and Marie Jois!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.74,0:22:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just about anyone can show up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.38,0:22:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marines are coming up the rear!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.36,0:22:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy acts at random!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.96,0:22:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trafalgar! Stay out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.71,0:22:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to be destroyed? I told \Nyou not to tell me what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.32,0:22:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're running into unexpected \Nbig-shots today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.00,0:22:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather not add an admiral to that list...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.00,0:23:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so you will let us pass...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.95,0:23:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Bartholomew Kuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.08,0:23:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were on the Pirate King's ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.61,0:23:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Pirate King was \Ncaught. How did you survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.75,0:23:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We weren't caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.70,0:23:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger turned himself in.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.80,0:23:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.77,0:23:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to know the whole story?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.22,0:23:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.85,0:23:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Roger and Rayleigh\N-- The King of the Pirates and His Right Hand Man"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.82,0:23:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
